[I] A HTML::Parser module from CPAN

[T] This is a collection of modules that parse and extract information
[T] from HTML documents. Bug reports and issues for discussion about
[T] these modules can be sent to the <libwww@perl.org> mailing list.
[T] Remember to also look at the HTML-Tree package that build on
[T] HTML::Parser to create and extract information from HTML syntax trees.
[T]
[T] spamassassin makes use of this module ...

